lands|accessdate=20 August 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Netherlands at the 2017 FIBA U16 European Championship Division B|url=https://www.fiba.basketball/europe/u16b/2017/Netherlands|accessdate=19 August 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Netherlands at the 2018 FIBA U16 European Championship|url=http://www.fiba.basketball/europe/u16/2018/team/Netherlands|accessdate=18 August 2018}}</ref> The current coach is [[Radenko Varagic]].\n\n==See also==\n*[[Netherlands national basketball team]]\n*[[Netherlands national under-19 basketball team]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.basketball.nl/ Official website] {{in lang|nl}}\n*[http://www.fiba.basketball/federation/Netherlands FIBA profile]\n\n{{International youth basketball}}\n{{National sports teams of the Netherlands}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Netherlands national under-19 basketball team}}\n[[Category:Basketball in the Netherlands]]\n[[Category:Basketball teams in the Netherlands]]\n[[Category:National under-16 basketball teams]]\n[[Category:National under-17 basketball teams]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox national basketball team\n| country            = Netherlands\n| logo               = Flag of Netherlands.svg\n| logo_width         = 130px\n| nickname           = Orange Lions\n| fiba_zone          = FIBA Europe\n| national_fed       = [[Basketball Nederland]]\n| coach              = [[Radenko Varagic]]\n| wc_championship    = [[FIBA Under-17 Basketball World Cup|Under-17 World Cup]]\n| wc_appearances     = None\n| wc_medals          = \n| zone_championship  = [[FIBA U16 European Championship|U16 European Championship]]\n| zone_appearances   = 1\n| zone_medals        = None\n| zone_championship2 = [[FIBA U16 European Championship#Division B|U16 European Championship Division B]]\n| zone_appearances2  = 15\n| zone_medals2       = {{Eur2}} ''Silver:'' ([[2017 FIBA U16 European Championship Division B|2017]], [[2019 FIBA U16 European Championship Division B|2019]])\n| h_body             = FF